Name: Battle Imagine - Void Foxen
Description:
Activates or advances the Battle Imagine skill of Mutant Foxen - Stunt! Spirit Fox Assault.

Stunt! Spirit Fox Assault
Resonates with the power of Elite Mutant Foxen, leaps into the air and swiftly pounces forward for a rapid kill, dealing area Attack Damage, and increases your haste bonus for 20s.
Description2: A crystallization of thoughts, consciousness, and Engram, possessing supernatural power. This principle has not been unraveled since the Bapharian civilization.
